| Simulation | {{ stages.simulation.status }} | {{ timestamp[:10] }} |
| Synthesis | {{ stages.synthesis.status }} | {{ timestamp[:10] }} |

**Interface:** `{{ interface_name or "generic" }}` |
**Technology:** `{{ technology }}` |
**VeriFlow:** `{{ veriflow_version }}`

## RTL Sources

| File | SHA256 |
|------|--------|
{% for file, hash in rtl_hash.items() %}
| `{{ file }}` | `{{ hash[:12] }}...` |
{% endfor %}

## Port Map

{# interface_ports is [] for a generic project (no interface configured) --
   show a plain status line instead of an empty/missing table. When
   interface_port_descriptions has any entries, add a 4th "Description"
   column; otherwise the table stays 3 columns (unchanged from before
   port_descriptions existed). #}
{% if interface_ports %}
{% if interface_port_descriptions %}
| Port | Direction | Width | Description |
|------|-----------|-------|-------------|
{% for port in interface_ports %}
| `{{ port.name }}` | {{ port.direction }} | {{ port.width }} | {{ interface_port_descriptions.get(port.name, "") }} |
{% endfor %}
{% else %}
| Port | Direction | Width |
|------|-----------|-------|
{% for port in interface_ports %}
| `{{ port.name }}` | {{ port.direction }} | {{ port.width }} |
{% endfor %}
{% endif %}
{% else %}
*No interface profile selected -- connectivity check skipped*
{% endif %}

